data.description: This beautiful home offers an open floor plan, creating a spacious and welcoming atmosphere. The updated kitchen features modern appliances and plenty of counter space, perfect for preparing delicious meals. You'll love the attention to detail throughout the house, as it has been lovingly cared for.  Move-in ready, this home also boasts a finished basement, providing additional living space for entertaining or relaxation. With three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, there's plenty of room for the whole family.  Stay cool in the summer with central air conditioning, and enjoy the convenience of off-street parking for two cars. This home is close to schools, shopping centers, public transportation, bridges, and I-95.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home!
